   "en": "Iekara Nigedashitai Watashi ga, Ukkari Akogare no Daimahoutsukai-sama wo Katteshimattara"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "家から逃げ出したい私が、うっかり憧れの大魔法使い様を買ってしまったら"
   },
   {
    "en": "That Time I Bought a Great Wizard in Hopes of Becoming a Runaway"
   },
   {
    "en": "In My Efforts to Runaway From Home, I Accidentally Bought the Great Sorcerer!"
   },
   {
    "zh": "想逃离家的我、不小心买下了仰慕的大魔法使大人"
   }
